description:
Just because I lack a few words to close above two thousand, I want to give you a conclusion, and it is quite cliché if you read the whole writing, because actually more than a conclusion is an allegory to life and how short it is, and taking into account that human life is over in a matter of seconds, I would just like to conclude that do not be afraid of life, or chaos, you do not know when your last day may be calm, better live a life of chaos and die happy, doing something worthwhile, do not die like the fish that was trapped in a still sea, better live a life you would like to remember.

“What with the fascinating things? Whats up that? Whats been on the stars? How long is it going on?”
The end.
